{"title": "Editing & Cancelling an Appointment from the Waiting Room", "body": "Editing an Appointment from the Waiting Room \nThis article will cover how to edit and cancel an appointment from the Waiting Room.\nTo edit an appointment of a patient that is in the Waiting Room, click the Patient Name to reveal a list of options for the appointment.\nClick Edit Appt.\nUpdate the appointment with all required changes and click Save.\nCancelling an Appointment from the Waiting Room\nTo cancel the appointment of a patient that is in the waiting room, click the Patient Name to reveal a list of options for the appointment.\nClick Cancel Appt to reveal a drop-down list of options.\nSelect the Reason for Cancellation from the drop-down list to cancel the appointment.\nThe patient will be removed from the Waiting Room, and the appointment will be canceled from Appointment Calendar."}